Just try to keep the total quantities the same. If you don't want to use quite so much coconut oil, reduce the quantity to 1/2 cup. Coconut oil can be substituted for macadamia oil. If substituting oils, reduce the amount in the recipe to 1/2 cup.\",\"datePublished\":\"2015-01-26T15:56:55+00:00\",\"image\":[\"//thecookspyjamas.com/wp-content/uploads/Coconut-Macadamia-Granola-2.jpg\",\"//thecookspyjamas.com/wp-content/uploads/Coconut-Macadamia-Granola-2-500x500.jpg\",\"//thecookspyjamas.com/wp-content/uploads/Coconut-Macadamia-Granola-2-500x375.jpg\",\"//thecookspyjamas.com/wp-content/uploads/Coconut-Macadamia-Granola-2-480x270.jpg\"],\"recipeYield\":[\"2\",\"2 x 1.5L containers\"],\"prepTime\":\"PT10M\",\"cookTime\":\"PT40M\",\"totalTime\":\"PT50M\",\"recipeIngredient\":[\"3 cups rolled oats (300g)\",\"1 cup rolled rye (130g)\",\"1 cup rolled barley (120g)\",\"1 1/2 cups macadamias (chopped, 120g)\",\"1 cup pecans (chopped, 100g)\",\"1 cup flaked coconut (65g)\",\"1/2 cup sunflower seeds (75g)\",\"1/2 cup pepitas (70g)\",\"3/4 cup melted coconut oil (180ml)\",\"1/4 cup rice bran syrup (60ml)\",\"1/4 cup maple syrup (60ml)\",\"2 teaspoons vanilla extract\",\"1 teaspoon ground cinnamon\",\"1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg\",\"Large pinch of salt\"],\"recipeInstructions\":[{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Preheat the oven to 160C (140C fan forced).\",\"name\":\"Preheat the oven to 160C (140C fan forced).\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-0\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Line two large trays with baking paper.\",\"name\":\"Line two large trays with baking paper.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-1\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Place the rolled grains, nuts, sunflower seeds, pepitas, and coconut in a large bowl. Stir through to combine.\",\"name\":\"Place the rolled grains, nuts, sunflower seeds, pepitas, and coconut in a large bowl. Stir through to combine.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-2\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Add the cinnamon, nutmeg and salt. In a separate bowl, place the coconut oil and the maple syrup and whisk to combine. Stir again to mix the spices through the grains.\",\"name\":\"Add the cinnamon, nutmeg and salt. In a separate bowl, place the coconut oil and the maple syrup and whisk to combine. Stir again to mix the spices through the grains.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-3\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Place the melted coconut oil, rice bran syrup and maple syrup into a small bowl or jug. Add the vanilla extract then stir until combined. The mixture will seem to thicken and emulsify.\",\"name\":\"Place the melted coconut oil, rice bran syrup and maple syrup into a small bowl or jug. Add the vanilla extract then stir until combined. The mixture will seem to thicken and emulsify.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-4\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Pour the liquids over the dry ingredients and stir until the muesli seems slightly damp.\",\"name\":\"Pour the liquids over the dry ingredients and stir until the muesli seems slightly damp.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-5\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Spread the mixture onto the lined trays.\",\"name\":\"Spread the mixture onto the lined trays.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-6\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Bake for about 30 - 40 minutes, stirring the edges of the mixture into the middle every 5 -10 minutes to ensure even baking.\",\"name\":\"Bake for about 30 - 40 minutes, stirring the edges of the mixture into the middle every 5 -10 minutes to ensure even baking.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-7\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Watch the muesli carefully towards the end of the baking time and check more frequently as it can burn easily.\",\"name\":\"Watch the muesli carefully towards the end of the baking time and check more frequently as it can burn easily.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-8\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"When golden brown, remove from the oven and allow to cool.\",\"name\":\"When golden brown, remove from the oven and allow to cool.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-9\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"text\":\"Store in an airtight container.\",\"name\":\"Store in an airtight container.\",\"url\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#wprm-recipe-6918-step-0-10\"}],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":\"5\",\"ratingCount\":\"3\"},\"recipeCategory\":[\"Breakfast\"],\"@id\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#recipe\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#article\"},\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://thecookspyjamas.com/coconut-macadamia-granola/#webpage\"}]}</script>"]},"aux":{"micro_s":1325},"tid":"2614029028166"}
